                      E_GW = E_SCF + Sigc(E_GW) + Sigx - vxc 
   
  Upper equation is solved self-consistently for E_GW, see Eq. (12) in J. Phys.
  Chem. Lett. 9, 306 (2018), doi: 10.1021/acs.jpclett.7b02740
  
  
